snippet: The U.S. men's national team cut John Wall, Bradley Beal and Paul Millsap on Monday, a person with knowledge of the details said, leaving the roster at 16 players....

headline.print_headline: AP Source: US Cuts Wall, Beal, Millsap, Down to 16
headline.main: AP Source: US Cuts Wall, Beal, Millsap, Down to 16

lead_paragraph: The U.S. men's national team cut John Wall, Bradley Beal and Paul Millsap on Monday, a person with knowledge of the details said, leaving the roster at 16 players.
